### ============================================================
### APIM Demo - REST Client Test File
### ============================================================
### Prerequisites:
###   1. Install "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client)
###   2. Get tokens by running the "Get Tokens" requests below first
### ============================================================

### Variables
@gatewayUrl = https://<YOUR_APIM_NAME>.azure-api.net
@subscriptionKey = <YOUR_SUBSCRIPTION_KEY>
@tenantId = <YOUR_TENANT_ID>
@apiAudience = api://<YOUR_API_APP_ID>
@adminClientId = <YOUR_ADMIN_CLIENT_ID>
@adminClientSecret = <YOUR_ADMIN_CLIENT_SECRET>
@userClientId = <YOUR_USER_CLIENT_ID>
@userClientSecret = <YOUR_USER_CLIENT_SECRET>

### Direct backend URLs (no APIM)
@functionUrl = https://<YOUR_FUNCTION_APP>.azurewebsites.net
@webApiUrl = https://<YOUR_WEB_APP>.azurewebsites.net


### ============================================================
### 1. GET TOKENS (run these first)
### ============================================================

### Get Admin Token
# @name adminLogin
POST https://login.microsoftonline.com/{{tenantId}}/oauth2/v2.0/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

client_id={{adminClientId}}&client_secret={{adminClientSecret}}&scope={{apiAudience}}/.default&grant_type=client_credentials

###

### Get User Token
# @name userLogin
POST https://login.microsoftonline.com/{{tenantId}}/oauth2/v2.0/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

client_id={{userClientId}}&client_secret={{userClientSecret}}&scope={{apiAudience}}/.default&grant_type=client_credentials

###

### Store tokens from responses above
@adminToken = {{adminLogin.response.body.access_token}}
@userToken = {{userLogin.response.body.access_token}}


### ============================================================
### 2. DIRECT BACKEND TESTS (no auth, no APIM)
### ============================================================

### Function App - Hello
GET {{functionUrl}}/api/hello

###

### Function App - Orders
GET {{functionUrl}}/api/orders

###

### Web API - Hello
GET {{webApiUrl}}/hello

###

### Web API - Products
GET {{webApiUrl}}/products

###

### Web API - Swagger
GET {{webApiUrl}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json

###


### ============================================================
### 3. APIM - Function API (with Admin token)
### ============================================================

### Function Hello via APIM
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/function/hello
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Function Orders via APIM
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/function/orders
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###


### ============================================================
### 4. APIM - Web API v1 (with Admin token)
### ============================================================

### Web API v1 - Hello
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/web/v1/hello
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Web API v1 - Products
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/web/v1/products
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###


### ============================================================
### 5. APIM - Web API v2 (with Admin token)
### ============================================================

### Web API v2 - Products
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/web/v2/products
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###


### ============================================================
### 6. APIM - Admin Endpoint (Role-Based Access)
### ============================================================

### Admin Health - with Admin token (expect 200)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/web/v1/admin/health
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Admin Health - with User token (expect 403 Forbidden)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/web/v1/admin/health
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###


### ============================================================
### 7. APIM - Legacy API (on-prem VM backend)
### ============================================================

### Legacy Customers (requires VM to be running)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/legacy/customers
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Legacy Status (requires VM to be running)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/legacy/status
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###


### ============================================================
### 8. ERROR CASES
### ============================================================

### No subscription key (expect 401)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/function/hello
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### No auth token (expect 401 - JWT validation fails)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/function/hello
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

###

### No credentials at all (expect 401)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/function/hello

###
